				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3 class="feature-title">üíù Personal Touch</h3>
				<p class="feature-description">
					Suggestions tailored to your partner's personality, interests, and love language. Every nudge feels personal and authentic.
				</p>
