			<div class="feature-card">
				<h3 class="feature-title">‚è∞ Perfect Timing</h3>
				<p class="feature-description">
					Smart scheduling that respects your routine. Suggestions arrive when you can actually act on them, not when it's inconvenient.
				</p>
			</div>

